{"tid":1345764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共最怕嘅係死狗鐵呀！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T03:34:30.000Z","uid":73392,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dac105fbe9b3ced9975abf162d4cdf5350e4b78f","tid":1345764,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:45:41.000Z","msg":"612之後柒婆未理大眾訴求，但係613，614嘅不合作運動，令狗鐵收皮，615柒婆就「暫緩」啦，狗鐵先係港共春袋呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">打鄉黑，敵暗我明，佢地隱藏於市，根本吹佢唔漲，仲未計刑事，同黑警選擇性執法</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞狗鐵，我暗敵明，我地隱於無形，佢地吹我地唔漲，黑警都唔知點nine你，低成本，高效益！！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講民意，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我屌柒你老母民意呀！！！</span>"},{"pid":"88e8ed70e3da72eebe78432288c6b3f96e6dffd9","tid":1345764,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"4c43f5c8bd3103cf51c581551632efe612e2675a","tid":1345764,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a45dc8032056d036ba89cdf692a32d806e81aad8","tid":1345764,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:10.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門呀"},{"pid":"e42407ce61f2ebed2ea9b768febc50fd16ebe737","tid":1345764,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"532d837c70c379dc59b97b40e4514c5009dc6eee","tid":1345764,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n今日成果不明顯"},{"pid":"29bcc11919c43dba029378456fe132059be78fe1","tid":1345764,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:51:10.000Z","msg":"柒婆咁快唔記得我地塞狗鐵，係0成本啦"},{"pid":"8a419322ca48dea4e6c519efb0f3c289966d12ec","tid":1345764,"uid":272461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"天減共匪"},{"pid":"6bf24126c69b82cc7cefdff2a0813c882a5622ad","tid":1345764,